title: What the Democrats told us about their fundraising numbers, and what it tells us about them
text: The dollar totals revealed as Wednesday night's fundraising deadline approached added some drama to the Democratic presidential contest -- and not just because, in the end, Hillary Rodham Clinton only barely out-raised underdog democratic socialist Bernie Sanders.
